<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.5.10">
<l>tārā vārum vayalcūḻnta cāḷak kirāmat taṭikaḷai</l>
<l>kārārp puṟaviṉ maṅkaivēntaṉ kaliya ṉolicey tamiḻmālai</l>
<l>ārā rulakat taṟivuṭaiyā ramarar nalnāṭ ṭaracāḷa</l>
<l>pērā yiramu mōtumiṅka ḷaṉṟi yivaiyē pitaṟṟumiṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Everyone who is wise in the world, to rule in the good realm of the immortals,</l>
<l>Chant [god’s] one-thousand names; otherwise,</l>
<l rend="indent">just jabber this garland of Tamil [verses]</l>
<l>Which Kaliyaṉ, king of Maṅkai with forests full of rainclouds, composed</l>
<l>About the deity of Śālagrāma, surrounded by heron-filled paddy fields.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
